examples.en: We cut through the neighbor's yard to get home sooner.
I baby-sit the neighbor's plants when she is out of town.
He looked at his neighbor's new car with unambiguous envy.
They put up a fence between their house and their neighbor's house.
The sound of music wafted softly into the yard from our neighbor's house.
He retaliated his neighbor's malicious destruction of his flower garden by cutting down the man's prize apple tree.
She was accused of hexing her neighbor's cows. *
The kid was bunging rocks through the neighbor's window. *
I ran over the neighbor's lawn with my car, so I'm really behind the eight ball. *
